dc_description_s: An ArcGIS Open Data Portal for the City of Evansville & Vanderburgh County, Indiana includes a large collection of downloadable geospatial resources.  Common dataset topics including parcels, roads, boundaries, and water resources are available, as are datasets covering many other subjects.  Aerial photography from several years between 2000-2016 are available for download, as well as elevation datasets from 2005 and 2014.
dc_title_s: Evansville, Vanderburgh County Open Data Portal
